<td class="article-body"><P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>
<TABLE cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 border=0>
<TBODY>
<TR>
<TD>
<P><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><U>Question Time with Marat</U></FONT></FONT></STRONG></P>
<P><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">How are you feeling these days?<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG>&nbsp;<SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Well as you can imagine I am feeling a bit down because of my last result and feeling of opportunities missed, however I am happy with the fact that I am healthy and not having pain in my knee.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></TD>
<TD>
<P align=center><IMG height=388 src="/Admin/spaw/DatabaseImages/ATha4AA.jpg" width=289 border=0></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD>
<P align=center><IMG height=280 src="/Admin/spaw/DatabaseImages/safin-marat5.jpg" width=205 border=0></P></TD>
<TD>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>How are you going to prepare for Paris and what do you feel are your chances for Roland Garros?<o:p></o:p></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">I am going to practice for a week in <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Valencia</st1:place></st1:country-region> on clay. I don’t think there is a better place to practice and work hard on my fitness. I enjoy being there.<BR>As to my chances in <st1:City w:st="on">Paris</st1:City> – well I always love playing in <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Paris</st1:place></st1:City>. Do not forget this is where my first breakthrough came about in 1998.I always come with lots of expectations in <st1:City w:st="on">Paris</st1:City> and maybe with no pressure and no seeding – with a few wins I might get the confidence to get a good result in <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Paris</st1:place></st1:City>!<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>What are your goals this year?<o:p></o:p></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">I really have to make short term goals at the moment.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">The first is to stay healthy – that is very important to me.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">2. I want to get a few wins in a row – that will give me the confidence I need.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">3. To be competitive in every match I play.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">4. With this to start to climb up the rankings so I can be seeded in the tournaments I play.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=2>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Do you feel there are any changes in the game after your 6 months absence with injury?<o:p></o:p></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Always coming back after a long break away – you feel the game is more quicker. I do not know if this is true or if I have to get used to it – it just feels like this. However I definitely see a transition of more young players such as Monfils, <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Murray</st1:place></st1:City>, Djokovic, Gasquet and Nadal is already there and the older guys they have be in shape as there is a lot more depth to the field in any tournament.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>How do you see <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Russia</st1:place></st1:country-region>’s chances in the Davis Cup this year?<o:p></o:p></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-GB style="mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">This is one of my biggest goals of the year and I have been thinking about it a lot. We have a good chance for the semi final against the <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">US</st1:place></st1:country-region> on clay at home. <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Russia</st1:place></st1:country-region> has a good team and lots of depth of players to choose from. Should we win the semi final we will play the final at home in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Moscow</st1:City></st1:place> and we have a good chance to win the cup for a second time.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></TD>
<TD>
<P align=center><IMG height=253 src="/Admin/spaw/DatabaseImages/DC0644a.jpg" width=250 border=0></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD></TD>
